{"tid":1986555,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美CDC新興傳染病學術月刊 拿清朝官服加蝙蝠當封面","createTime":"2020-04-24T02:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:38:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a75fafc2f545ca1b026ceaee4b57fd6e0c0dfadb","tid":1986555,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"美CDC新興傳染病學術月刊 拿清朝官服加蝙蝠當封面<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3144026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3144026&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hT%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=e6b37a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3144026&h=d18a6ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3144026</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/24/phphJsYxI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F24%2FphphJsYxI.jpg&h=3f5dce99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國境內武漢肺炎疫情趨緩，遂開始將心力放在對外宣傳，試圖透過輿論洗白形象，切割新型冠狀病毒發源地的形象。但這樣的做法似乎成效不彰，近日美國疾病管制與預防中心（CDC）所發布的學術月刊中，使用中國清朝官服「繡豹圖」連結武漢肺炎疫情，再度加深病毒與中國的連結。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CDC更新5月份《新興傳染病》學術月刊，封面用的卻是充滿中國意象的「繡豹圖」，並在圖中加入數隻蝙蝠。封面故事中寫道，「根據密歇根大學藝術博物館指出，在中國明朝，豹和虎是三品、四品官員的象徵；到了清朝前期，虎晉升為三品官的標誌。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文中指出，代表其它位階官員的形象還有鳥類和各種動物，含有散播人畜共通病原體的能力，導致人類感染呼吸道症狀，例如蝙蝠在古中國是好運的象徵，但其體內帶有立百病毒和亨德拉病毒，亦是嚴重急性呼吸道症候群（SARS）的源頭。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文末寫道，人類、動物、植物和環境的多重互動因素，為病毒創造了大量的機會，新型冠狀病毒即是一例，「一個人的位階可能讓他如魚得水，但這無法保護他免受新冠病毒或其它疾病的感染。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">丹麥主流媒體《日德蘭郵報》先前發布一篇名為「冠狀病毒」的投稿漫畫，將中國五星旗的五星畫為病毒圖案，諷刺意味明顯，且瀏覽數衝到該網站第一名，引發中國官方極度不滿。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"370d2b883f1f1a02153f509b18e0185f05505f9e","tid":1986555,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"又畫得幾靚"},{"pid":"4d5a1ed67a12cd70b8715d39e8adf45ed6b77343","tid":1986555,"uid":204539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:22:28.000Z","msg":"啲桃係咪乳頭同屎忽嘅隱喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a96732a2d051f2892de6617612e8f7f5cff329b","tid":1986555,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e99e3f5cc2e21699dcb409f1e9c325066949eff","tid":1986555,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138b1ecc82146faeb50e32927a3f4b1f0c5aa5f2","tid":1986555,"uid":189046,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOm839A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOm839A.jpg&h=9a07ba0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbd36ac0b6949e1ee98c7a2984f2c9e3992433e7","tid":1986555,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"咁撚串 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044d2fcfe8f149badf83cef7b4bd